                    This Privacy Statement (“Privacy Statement") by XIVA International Health Solutions, OPC. (“XIVA”, “xivahealth” “we”, or “us”) applies to persons who use directly or through another the xivahealth app in (1) requesting medical, nursing care, physical therapy care, diagnostics, laboratory, medicine delivery, telehealth service or other on-demand services (the “Services”) by users (collectively “Users”) or (2) accepting bookings for such services by doctors, nurses, physical therapists, and other medical professionals (the “Medical Professionals”). Client(s) shall include the User, his/her direct ascendants, descendants and/or siblings, (collectively, “Family Members”), and minors of whom the User exercises legal guardianship, as registered by the User with the xivahealth application. Users, Clients, and Medical Professionals shall be collectively referred to herein as “you”.

